-- Gold for Immediate Delivery Drops to $1,383.15, Extending Last Week's Fall
-- B y   W e n d y   P u g h
-- 2010-12-12T23:09:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-12/gold-for-immediate-delivery-drops-to-1-383-15-extending-last-week-s-fall.html
Gold for immediate delivery fell 0.2
percent to $1,383.15 an ounce at 10:02 a.m. Melbourne time after
dropping last week amid concern that China may tighten monetary
policy. Silver for immediate delivery declined 0.3 percent to
$28.60 an ounce.  To contact the reporter on this story:
